WEBVTT

1
00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:50.950
<i>In days of legend,</i>
<i>在传说时代</i>


2
00:00:51.990 --> 00:00:54.280
<i>gods walked the Earth...</i>
<i>神明在凡间穿巡....</i>


3
00:00:55.830 --> 00:00:58.040
<i>and tormented mortals.</i>
<i>摧残凡人</i>


4
00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:04.340
<i>Athena, goddess of warfare and wisdom,</i>
<i>雅典娜, 战争与智慧之女神</i>


5
00:01:04.420 --> 00:01:07.260
<i>had the power to destroy humanity,</i>
<i>明明拥有毁灭人类的力量,</i>


6
00:01:07.340 --> 00:01:09.370
<i>but chose to protect us.</i>
<i>却选择了保护我们</i>


7
00:01:10.340 --> 00:01:13.300
<i>Brave young knights from across the globe</i>
<i>来自世界各地的勇敢的年轻圣斗士们</i>


8
00:01:13.390 --> 00:01:15.970
<i>swore their allegiance to her.</i>N<i>宣誓效忠于她</i>

9
00:01:16.060 --> 00:01:17.640
<i>They learned to harness Cosmo...</i>
<i>他们学会了驾驭小宇宙....</i>


10
00:01:19.270 --> 00:01:21.060
<i>the power of the stars.</i>
<i>星辰的力量</i>


11
00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:24.900
<i>Their fists cracked to the heavens</i>
<i>他们的拳头划破了云霄</i>


12
00:01:24.980 --> 00:01:28.070
<i>in battles against those who wished Athena dead.</i>
<i>在与那些意图杀害雅典娜的敌人的战斗中</i>


13
00:01:32.240 --> 00:01:33.450
<i>Over time...</i>
<i>星转斗移....</i>


14
00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:37.410
<i>the gods retreated and became myths.</i>
<i>众神退隐, 成为神话</i>


15
00:01:38.450 --> 00:01:40.870
<i>But then, 18 years ago,</i>
<i>但是, 18 年前,</i>


16
00:01:40.960 --> 00:01:44.960
<i>Athena was reborn as a helpless child.</i>
<i>雅典娜获得重生 成了一个无助的婴儿</i>


17
00:01:46.130 --> 00:01:49.630
<i>A knight clad in gold armor</i>
<i>一名黄金圣斗士</i>


18
00:01:49.700 --> 00:01:53.450
<i>gave his life to protect her as they crashed to Earth.</i>
<i>在他们坠落到凡间之时, 献出生命保护了她</i>


19
00:01:55.460 --> 00:01:59.210
<i>And that's how I found her, lying in his arms.</i>
<i>就这样 我发现了她 躺在他怀里</i>


20
00:01:59.350 --> 00:02:02.020
<i>A mortal girl with the power of a god.</i>
<i>一个拥有神之力量的凡人女孩</i>


21
00:02:02.940 --> 00:02:04.230
<i>Since then,</i>
<i>从那时起</i>


22
00:02:04.320 --> 00:02:07.950
<i>I've been searching for a new generation of knights</i>
<i>我就一直在寻找新一代的圣斗士</i>


23
00:02:08.030 --> 00:02:10.610
<i>to protect Athena and the Earth.</i>
<i>来保护雅典娜和地球</i>


24
00:02:11.270 --> 00:02:18.470
《圣斗士星矢》
字幕:Dex7er  公众号:值得看的


25
00:02:20.820 --> 00:02:24.830
<i>We fight to protect ourselves.</i>
<i>我们是为了保护自己而战斗</i>


26
00:02:30.380 --> 00:02:32.840
<i>But we also fight to protect each other.</i>
<i>但我们也是为了保护彼此而战斗</i>


27
00:02:37.880 --> 00:02:40.670
<i>There's always something bigger than you, Seiya.</i>
<i>还有比你自己更重要的东西, 星矢</i>


28
00:02:41.190 --> 00:02:43.820
<i>You'll have to fight to protect that as well.</i>
<i>你也必须为了保护它而战斗</i>


29
00:02:51.150 --> 00:02:52.310
