你投降了？


30
00:02:52.580 --> 00:02:53.530
<i>Never!</i>
<i>绝不！</i>


31
00:02:56.490 --> 00:02:58.570
Nice try. But not tonight.
干的漂亮 但今晚不行


32
00:02:58.610 --> 00:03:00.240
- Tap out. - No!
- 认输 - 不


33
00:03:00.260 --> 00:03:01.930
You must learn when to quit!
你必须学会何时放弃！


34
00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:03.500
Never!
绝不！


35
00:03:07.830 --> 00:03:09.710
No, Seiya! Don't!
不 星矢 不要


36
00:03:11.550 --> 00:03:12.880
Promise you won't come out.
答应我 你别出来


37
00:03:13.170 --> 00:03:14.090
I promise.
我保证


38
00:03:25.800 --> 00:03:26.880
Hey, kid!
嘿, 孩子


39
