为野兽贾基鼓掌！


48
00:04:29.670 --> 00:04:39.660
<i>Jaki! Jaki! Jaki!</i>
<i>贾基！贾基！贾基！</i>


49
00:04:40.090 --> 00:04:43.470
And the contender, who literally danced his way
而这位竞争者, 简直就是靠跳舞


50
00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:45.430
to through his first two fights,
通过了前两场比赛


51
00:04:45.940 --> 00:04:49.940
let's hear it for Street Kid Seiya!
让我们为街头小子星矢欢呼！


52
00:04:55.610 --> 00:04:57.110
You both know how this works.
你们都知道这是什么地方


53
00:04:59.520 --> 00:05:02.030
You know the rules. There are none.
你们知道规则 就是没有规则


54
00:05:02.280 --> 00:05:04.950
Anything goes until one of you gives up or blacks out.
任何招式都可以, 直到你们其中一个投降或昏倒


55
00:05:06.910 --> 00:05:10.000
If you give up, you're banished from the Octagon.
如果你投降, 就会被逐出八角笼


56
00:05:10.080 --> 00:05:11.500
Understood?
明白了吗？


57
00:05:32.020 --> 00:05:33.110
Damn it, fight!
该死的, 打啊！


58
00:05:36.690 --> 00:05:38.780
Hey! I said, no dancing!
我说了, 不许跳舞


59
00:06:04.010 --> 00:06:06.760
<i>Cassios! Cassios! Cassios!</i>
<i>卡西欧士 卡西欧士 卡西欧士</i>


60
00:06:06.850 --> 00:06:08.890
What, you think you can just ignore me?
怎么, 你以为你可以无视我？


61
00:06:09.730 --> 00:06:11.100
Okay, calm down, big guy.
好了, 冷静点, 大个子


62
00:06:26.070 --> 00:06:27.490
Ballet's over, kid.
芭蕾结束了, 孩子


63
00:06:58.390 --> 00:07:00.350
Cassios wins.
卡西欧士赢了


64
00:07:00.440 --> 00:07:01.530
Every...
每...


65
00:07:01.610 --> 00:07:02.780
single...
一...


66
00:07:02.860 --> 00:07:03.860
time.
次


67
00:07:09.950 --> 00:07:15.960
<i>Cassios! Cassios! Cassios!</i>
<i>卡西欧士 卡西欧士 卡西欧士</i>


68
00:07:38.460 --> 00:07:39.670
You give up?
你投降了？


69
00:08:16.810 --> 00:08:17.810
Yeah!
耶


70
00:08:35.280 --> 00:08:36.780
You don't know when to quit, huh?
你不知道什么时候该投降, 是吧？


71
00:08:38.250 --> 00:08:39.250
Yeah.
是啊


72
00:08:39.780 --> 00:08:40.990
I've heard that before.
我以前就听说过


73
00:08:57.640 --> 00:08:59.270
We're not done here!
我们还没完！


74
00:09:03.980 --> 00:09:05.320
This ain't over!
这还没完！


75
00:09:17.040 --> 00:09:18.160
Come outside.
到外面来


76
00:09:19.410 --> 00:09:22.040
You're cute, but you're not my type, man.
你很可爱, 但不是我喜欢的类型, 伙计


77
00:09:26.170 --> 00:09:30.340
There's someone outside that wants to speak with you.
外面有人想和你聊聊


78
00:09:30.430 --> 00:09:32.050
He knows about your search.
他知道你在找人


79
00:09:34.080 --> 00:09:35.920
He knows what you're looking for.
他知道你在找什么


80
00:09:51.570 --> 00:09:52.570
Give me that.
给我


81
00:10:00.040 --> 00:10:01.250
Yeah, it's me.
是我


82
00:10:04.170 --> 00:10:06.550
Think I found one of your Cosmo guys.
我想我发现了一个你要的圣斗士


83
00:10:19.660 --> 00:10:20.660
I'm out of here.
我要走了


84
00:10:22.310 --> 00:10:25.270
Your little show in there made some people upset.
你在那里的小表演让一些人不高兴了


85
00:10:25.540 --> 00:10:27.220
Look, I'm not looking for trouble.
听着, 我不是来找麻烦的


86
00:10:27.510 --> 00:10:29.640
You may not be looking, but you've found it.
也许你不是, 但麻烦已经找到你了


87
00:10:30.650 --> 00:10:34.110
In a few moments, Vander Guraad will be here with her boys.
再过几分钟, 范德·古拉杜就会带着她的手下们来了


88
00:10:35.480 --> 00:10:36.480
Who?
谁？


89
00:10:37.160 --> 00:10:38.370
My ex- wife.
我的前妻


90
00:10:38.630 --> 00:10:40.250
She controls this fighting ring.
她控制着这个格斗场


91
00:10:40.280 --> 00:10:42.160
It's her recruitment operation.
这是她的招集障眼法


92
00:10:43.140 --> 00:10:44.940
What do you mean? What does she recruit?
什么意思？招集什么？


93
00:10:45.090 --> 00:10:47.460
Warriors with special skills.
拥有特殊技能的战士


94
00:10:47.560 --> 00:10:48.960
For her private army.
组建她的私人军队


95
00:10:50.170 --> 00:10:51.090
Okay.
好吧


96
00:10:51.170 --> 00:10:52.840
I saw what you did in the ring.
我看到了你在擂台上的表现


97
00:10:53.590 --> 00:10:55.980
I knew it had to be you, Seiya.
我就知道一定是你, 星矢


98
00:10:59.350 --> 00:11:00.350
Who are you?
你是谁？


99
00:11:01.440 --> 00:11:03.190
I'm the only friend you have.
我是你唯一的朋友


100
00:11:04.850 --> 00:11:06.560
You need to make a choice, Seiya.
你得做个选择了, 星矢


101
00:11:06.650 --> 00:11:10.110
Come with me or try your luck against Guraad's warriors.
跟我走, 要不就跟古拉杜的战士们碰碰运气


102
00:11:16.200 --> 00:11:17.530
Lead the way.
带路


103
00:11:24.750 --> 00:11:25.830
Come on!
来吧


104
00:11:36.260 --> 00:11:37.830
Look what we've found.
看看我们发现了什么


105
00:11:47.310 --> 00:11:48.650
What are those guys made of?
那些家伙是什么做的？


106
00:11:48.730 --> 00:11:50.440
You don't want to know. Keep moving!
你不会想知道的 继续走


107
00:12:04.230 --> 00:12:05.970
Our ride's just around the corner!
我们的接应就在街角


108
00:12:11.710 --> 00:12:12.840
Get down!
趴下


109
00:12:29.900 --> 00:12:31.060
Go!
走


110
00:12:33.030 --> 00:12:35.150
Meet Mylock, my assistant.
这是晨己, 我的助手


111
00:12:40.070 --> 00:12:42.200
Those guys work for your ex- wife?
那些家伙是给你前妻工作的？


112
00:12:42.790 --> 00:12:44.370
Surrender the boy!
交出那小子


113
00:12:50.050 --> 00:12:51.880
Dude, you gotta make better life choices.
老兄, 你该选一个更好的老婆


114
00:13:01.090 --> 00:13:02.550
What the hell is that thing?
那到底是什么东西？


115
00:13:06.970 --> 00:13:08.470
Hope you had a light dinner.
希望你晚上吃得不多


116
00:13:35.550 --> 00:13:36.550
Why are they after me?
他们为什么要抓我？


117
00:13:36.630 --> 00:13:38.550
They're after warriors with a strong Cosmo.
他们要抓的是拥有强大小宇宙的战士


118
00:13:43.760 --> 00:13:45.810
Cosmo? Is that a new martial arts or something?
小宇宙？那是一种新门派还是什么？


119
00:13:46.450 --> 00:13:48.860
You should know. You tapped into it in the Octagon.
你应该知道 你在八角笼里就已经觉醒过了


120
00:13:48.890 --> 00:13:51.110
I didn't tap into anything. They got the wrong guy!
我什么也没有觉醒过 他们抓错人了


121
00:13:51.170 --> 00:13:53.300
Oh, would you like us to stop and let them know?
哦, 你想停下来告诉他们吗？


122
00:14:05.870 --> 00:14:06.870
God!
上帝啊


123
00:14:26.260 --> 00:14:27.640
Hold on tight!
抓紧了


124
00:14:46.350 --> 00:14:49.070
I am not going another step until you tell me what's going on.
除非你告诉我发生了什么事, 不然我不会再走一步了


125
00:14:49.260 --> 00:14:50.970
There'll be time for that later.
以后有得是时间告诉你


126
00:14:51.610 --> 00:14:53.050
We're still in danger.
我们还没脱离危险


127
00:14:53.420 --> 00:14:54.800
You're really...
你真的...


128
00:15:00.050 --> 00:15:02.630
<i>Okay, okay, okay. Go to sleep.</i>
<i>好吧 睡吧</i>


129
00:15:19.320 --> 00:15:21.230
Hey. Hey. Wake up. Wake up.
嘿 醒醒


130
00:15:22.640 --> 00:15:24.000
Wake up. Come on.
醒醒 快来


131
00:15:26.900 --> 00:15:29.860
You need to hide. No matter what happens, you stay out of sight.
你要躲起来 无论发生什么 都不要出来


132
00:15:29.990 --> 00:15:32.410
I have to make sure these people don't find you.
我必须确保这些人不会找到你


133
00:15:32.500 --> 00:15:33.960
Promise you won't come out.
答应我你别出来


134
00:15:34.750 --> 00:15:36.920
Okay. I promise.
好的 我保证


135
00:16:05.020 --> 00:16:05.960
Thank you.
谢谢


136
00:16:06.590 --> 00:16:07.590
For what?
为了什么？


137
00:16:09.780 --> 00:16:11.480
You tapped into your Cosmo.
你觉醒了你的小宇宙


138
00:16:12.580 --> 00:16:14.910
<i>No, Seiya. Don't!</i>
<i>不 星矢 不要</i>


139
00:16:17.620 --> 00:16:19.580
<i>Led me right to your doorstep.</i>
<i>指引我到了你家门口</i>


140
00:16:19.870 --> 00:16:22.700
检测到能量资源
目标


141
00:16:24.340 --> 00:16:26.470
Saved me so much trouble.
给我省了很多麻烦


142
00:16:30.430 --> 00:16:31.260
Let's go!
我们走吧


143
00:16:31.850 --> 00:16:32.680
Let's go!
我们走吧


144
00:16:32.760 --> 00:16:35.270
You can't use it. Only the Pegasus can!
你用不了的 只有天马座才可以


145
00:16:35.350 --> 00:16:36.980
That's why you're coming with us.
这就是为什么你要跟我们走


146
00:17:02.710 --> 00:17:03.750
Relax.
放松


147
00:17:05.050 --> 00:17:06.460
Relax, we're safe now.
放松, 我们现在安全了


148
00:17:07.420 --> 00:17:08.450
Safe?
安全？


149
00:17:08.550 --> 00:17:10.300
First I get attacked by ninja cyborgs,
我先被忍者机器人袭击


150
00:17:10.350 --> 00:17:12.020
then I got a spaceship shooting at me.
然后就有一艘飞船朝我开火


151
00:17:12.180 --> 00:17:14.350
And then that freak in a suit drugs me!
再然后那个穿西装的怪胎给我下了药


152
00:17:14.670 --> 00:17:16.970
Allow me to rephrase it.
请允许我换一种说法


153
00:17:17.060 --> 00:17:19.100
You're safer here than with Guraad.
你在这里会比跟着古拉杜更安全


154
00:17:19.250 --> 00:17:21.730
She has already captured many kids like you,
她已经抓走了很多像你一样的孩子


155
00:17:21.810 --> 00:17:23.070
drained them of their Cosmo.
吸干了他们的小宇宙


156
00:17:23.110 --> 00:17:25.410
Stop talking nonsense and tell me what's going on!
别再胡说八道了, 告诉我到底怎么回事！


157
00:17:26.070 --> 00:17:27.650
- Prepare for landing. - What?
- 准备着陆 - 什么？


158
00:17:27.740 --> 00:17:30.030
You might want to buckle up.
你最好系好安全带


159
00:17:30.110 --> 00:17:31.280
No, I want answers now!
不, 我现在就要答案！


160
00:17:32.070 --> 00:17:33.160
Oh, shit.
哦, 该死


161
00:17:40.120 --> 00:17:41.380
There's no runway!
没跑道啊


162
00:17:44.630 --> 00:17:46.210
I said, you might want to buckle up.
我说过, 你最好系上安全带


163
00:17:56.720 --> 00:17:59.230
You couldn't just tell me this thing lands vertically?
你就不能告诉我这东西是垂直降落的吗？


164
00:18:06.150 --> 00:18:07.990
Let's start afresh, shall we?
让我们重新开始, 好吗？


165
00:18:08.610 --> 00:18:10.530
My name is Alman Kido.
我叫城户光政


166
00:18:10.610 --> 00:18:13.320
Once upon a time, I was a businessman.
从前, 我是一个商人


167
00:18:13.400 --> 00:18:15.860
Mylock, let her know our guest has arrived, please.
晨己, 请告诉她我们的客人到了


168
00:18:15.950 --> 00:18:17.120
Yes, sir.
是的, 先生


169
00:18:17.620 --> 00:18:19.620
Should I believe you went bust?
我应该相信你破产了吗？


170
00:18:19.750 --> 00:18:24.090
I won't hide the fact I've been quite successful in my trade.
不瞒你说, 我的生意做得相当成功


171
00:18:24.370 --> 00:18:27.160
But the one thing money can't buy is purpose.
但有一样东西是金钱买不到的, 那就是使命


172
00:18:27.500 --> 00:18:30.000
So this is where you store your "purpose"?
这就是你存放"使命"的地方？


173
00:18:30.550 --> 00:18:31.550
Yes.
是的


174
00:18:34.950 --> 00:18:36.750
Tell me, Seiya, what do you see?
告诉我, 星矢, 你看到了什么？


175
00:18:40.200 --> 00:18:41.360
I'm not sure.
我不确定


176
00:18:41.950 --> 00:18:44.460
A whole bunch of real old stuff, I guess.
一大堆真正的古董 我猜


177
00:18:45.520 --> 00:18:47.150
I see stories.
我看到的是故事


178
00:18:47.390 --> 00:18:51.880
Ancient heroes were defined by their monumental deeds
古代英雄是由他们的不朽事迹


179
00:18:51.900 --> 00:18:53.950
as much as by their tragic ends.
和他们的悲剧结局所定义的


180
00:18:54.990 --> 00:18:59.540
I always admired the formidable magnitude of their fate.
我一直钦佩他们命运的伟大


181
00:18:59.910 --> 00:19:05.290
I envied it. I used to think the ancient lore held no secret for me.
我很羡慕 我曾经以为古老的传说对我来说没有什么秘密


182
00:19:07.090 --> 00:19:08.860
I'm afraid that was my hubris.
恐怕是我太傲慢了


183
00:19:10.550 --> 00:19:12.420
What do you know about Athena?
你对雅典娜了解多少？


184
00:19:12.510 --> 00:19:15.380
- She was a god of war. - And wisdom.
- 她是战争之神 - 也是智慧之神


185
00:19:15.550 --> 00:19:18.640
What if I told you Athena had returned in human form
如果我告诉你 雅典娜重回人间了


186
00:19:18.810 --> 00:19:22.980
and you are destined to become one of her guardian knights?
而你注定要成为她的守护圣斗士之一呢？


187
00:19:23.420 --> 00:19:25.790
I'd say your therapist isn't worth his paycheck.
我得说, 你的心理医生配不上你付他的薪水


188
00:19:26.940 --> 00:19:29.090
Things happen for a reason, Seiya.
事出必有因, 星矢


189
00:19:29.380 --> 00:19:31.090
Your Cosmo brought you here.
是你的小宇宙把你带到这里来的


190
00:19:31.140 --> 00:19:33.810
Actually, I was brought here on a very expensive aircraft.
事实上, 我是乘坐一架非常昂贵的飞机来的


191
00:19:34.450 --> 00:19:36.450
And now I'm leaving on my own two feet.
现在, 我要靠自己的双脚离开了


192
00:19:38.700 --> 00:19:40.660
You know the truth in your heart, Seiya.
你心底知道真相, 星矢


193
00:19:41.120 --> 00:19:42.620
Your sister knew it too.
你姐姐也知道


194
00:19:51.000 --> 00:19:52.760
What do you know about my sister?
你对我姐姐了解多少？


195
00:19:52.850 --> 00:19:56.850
Ten years ago, 
Guraad detected a strong Cosmo

196
00:19:56.930 --> 00:19:59.050
at your location. She thought it was Patricia.
在你家那里 她以为是星华


197
00:19:59.080 --> 00:20:00.410
What did she do to her?
她对她做了什么？


198
00:20:00.520 --> 00:20:03.750
I don't know, but your sister gave herself up
我不知道, 但你姐姐拿自己顶上了


199
00:20:03.850 --> 00:20:05.880
so that Guraad wouldn't find you.
这样古拉杜就不会去找你


200
00:20:06.220 --> 00:20:08.810
She knew what you were to become.
她知道你的天命所归


201
00:20:08.900 --> 00:20:11.730
A warrior of Athena. The Pegasus Knight.
雅典娜的战士 天马座圣斗士


202
00:20:12.350 --> 00:20:13.630
The Pegasus Knight?
天马座圣斗士？


203
00:20:14.290 --> 00:20:15.880
You're really out of your mind.
你真是疯了


204
00:20:17.200 --> 00:20:18.950
That doesn't bode well.
这可不是什么好兆头


205
00:20:19.290 --> 00:20:20.540
This is Sienna.
这是沙织


206
00:20:21.740 --> 00:20:24.000
Guraad is after her too.
古拉杜也在追杀她


207
00:20:24.090 --> 00:20:25.670
Your mission is to protect her.
你的任务是保护她


208
00:20:25.790 --> 00:20:27.170
I can take care of myself.
我能照顾好自己


209
00:20:27.200 --> 00:20:29.870
Why would I ever want to risk my neck to protect some rich girl?
我为什么要冒着生命危险去保护一个富家千金？


210
00:20:31.290 --> 00:20:35.230
Because our little Sienna here is the reincarnation of the goddess Athena.
因为我们的小沙织就是雅典娜女神转世


211
00:20:35.260 --> 00:20:38.300
- Dad. - Don't you have something for our guest?
- 爸爸 - 你不是有东西要给我们的客人吗？


212
00:20:38.460 --> 00:20:40.880
Sure, a toilet, so he can flush himself out.
当然, 给个厕所, 这样他就能把自己冲走了


213
00:20:41.090 --> 00:20:43.380
Wow, spoken like a true goddess.
哇, 说得像个真正的女神


214
00:20:43.570 --> 00:20:47.530
Dad, come on. This moron can't seriously be the Pegasus Knight.
爸爸, 别这样，这个白痴不可能真的是天马座圣斗士


215
00:20:48.940 --> 00:20:49.940
Go on.
去吧


216
00:20:53.580 --> 00:20:54.700
Fine.
很好


217
00:20:55.040 --> 00:20:57.250
You might recognize this, Seiya.
你可能认得这个, 星矢


218
00:21:11.420 --> 00:21:12.500
This is Patricia's.
这是星华的


219
00:21:13.420 --> 00:21:16.090
That is the key to the Pegasus armor.
这就是天马圣衣的钥匙


220
00:21:16.170 --> 00:21:18.920
Without it, you don't stand a chance against Guraad's army.
没有圣衣, 想要对抗古拉杜的大军, 你根本没有机会


221
00:21:19.080 --> 00:21:20.360
I could've handled those guys.
我可以对付那些家伙


222
00:21:20.680 --> 00:21:22.180
That's not what Mylock said.
晨己可不是这么说的


223
00:21:25.620 --> 00:21:28.140
So how's this supposed to help me find my sister?
这个要怎么才能帮我找到我姐姐？


224
00:21:28.230 --> 00:21:30.690
You give me a little present and expect me to help you out?
给我一个小礼物, 就指望我会帮你？


225
00:21:30.730 --> 00:21:32.730
My plan is to trust you to do what is right.
我的计划是相信你会做正确的事


226
00:21:32.770 --> 00:21:33.980
And what would that be?
那是什么呢？


227
00:21:34.150 --> 00:21:37.440
I suppose you've never heard of Marin, the Silver Knight.
我想你从未听说过白银圣斗士魔铃吧


228
00:21:37.520 --> 00:21:39.270
God, another one of your old legends?
天哪, 又一个你的古老传说？


229
00:21:39.360 --> 00:21:41.660
Marin can teach you how to reveal
魔铃可以教你如何揭示


230
00:21:41.740 --> 00:21:43.470
the hidden secret of the pendant.
那个吊坠的秘密


231
00:21:43.670 --> 00:21:46.460
So you can protect Sienna, and yourself, against your enemies.
这样你就能保护沙织, 和你自己, 对抗敌人


232
00:21:46.640 --> 00:21:48.540
And maybe even help you find your sister.
也许还能帮你找到你姐姐


233
00:21:48.600 --> 00:21:50.260
Ancient gods. Magic knights.
古代诸神 魔法斗士


234
00:21:50.330 --> 00:21:52.830
Do you have any idea how totally insane you sound?
你知道你听起来有多疯狂吗？


235
00:21:52.960 --> 00:21:56.510
I know, it is a lot to take in, isn't it?
我知道, 这很难接受, 不是吗？


236
00:21:56.590 --> 00:22:00.430
So why don't we have breakfast, take the day off and...
那么, 我们为什么不吃点早餐, 休息一天, 然后...


237
00:22:01.440 --> 00:22:03.610
revisit this tomorrow. Yeah.
明天再看 嗯


238
00:22:07.060 --> 00:22:08.770
Well, I am hungry, but...
我饿了, 但是...


239
00:22:08.850 --> 00:22:11.110
A goddess's fate is on the line, but sure.
女神的命运岌岌可危, 但是好吧


240
00:22:11.150 --> 00:22:12.960
Let's eat pancakes.
我们去吃煎饼吧


241
00:22:14.510 --> 00:22:15.350
Yeah.
对


242
00:22:25.990 --> 00:22:27.910
Get off my ring, you scum.
从我的擂台上滚开, 你这个人渣


243
00:22:28.750 --> 00:22:29.960
Get out of my ring!
滚出我的擂台


244
00:22:31.370 --> 00:22:32.960
You moron.
你个白痴


245
00:22:33.040 --> 00:22:35.070
You were supposed to keep a low profile.
你应该保持低调


246
00:22:35.710 --> 00:22:36.920
And I did.
我做到了


247
00:22:37.170 --> 00:22:39.210
We need to shut this place down.
我们得把这地方关掉


248
00:22:39.300 --> 00:22:42.720
- You don't get to decide that! - That's right. I do.
- 这不是你能决定的 - 没错 我可以


249
00:22:42.790 --> 00:22:44.380
Guraad, come on.
古拉杜, 别


250
00:22:45.140 --> 00:22:46.600
We have a great partnership.
我们合作得很好


251
00:22:46.730 --> 00:22:48.560
Yes. We did.
是的 是的


252
00:22:49.640 --> 00:22:51.560
How's the boy's Cosmo?
那小子的小宇宙怎么样？


253
00:22:51.640 --> 00:22:52.980
It's legit.
很正宗


254
00:22:53.140 --> 00:22:56.140
Good news. I've got a new deal for you.
好消息 我有一个新交易给你


255
00:22:56.930 --> 00:22:58.820
No ring, no deal.
没有擂台, 就没有交易


256
00:22:58.900 --> 00:22:59.780
All the better.
那就更好了


257
00:22:59.860 --> 00:23:02.850
Nobody needs a loser who gets his ass kicked by a scrawny little kid.
没有人会需要一个 被一个小毛孩子打得屁滚尿流的失败者


258
00:23:02.930 --> 00:23:04.590
He got a lucky break.
他很走运


259
00:23:04.820 --> 00:23:06.980
No man gets lucky twice with Cassios.
没有人能在卡西欧士身上走运两次


260
00:23:07.070 --> 00:23:09.570
I can beat anyone, anytime.
我随时都能击败任何人


261
00:23:09.660 --> 00:23:11.040
Well, let's see if that's true.
让我们看看这是不是真的


262
00:23:29.330 --> 00:23:30.450
Something wrong?
有什么问题吗？


263
00:23:34.000 --> 00:23:37.170
I just don't know how you can breathe while you're eating like that.
我真不知道就你那种吃法怎么还能呼吸的


264
00:23:40.900 --> 00:23:44.150
Where I come from, you eat as much as you can, when you can.
在我们那里, 有东西吃的时候, 能吃多少就吃多少


265
00:23:46.040 --> 00:23:48.250
You never know where your next meal's coming from.
你永远不知道下一顿饭在哪里


266
00:23:52.190 --> 00:23:53.450
You wouldn't understand.
你不会明白的


267
00:23:56.170 --> 00:23:57.170
Rich girl.
富家千金


268
00:23:59.960 --> 00:24:01.340
No, I wouldn't.
不, 我不会


269
00:24:02.590 --> 00:24:04.300
But I'm sorry you had to live like that.
但我很遗憾你不得不那样生活


270
00:24:09.600 --> 00:24:12.100
Sir. There's an urgent call.
先生 有紧急电话


271
00:24:13.730 --> 00:24:15.060
Please excuse me.
请原谅


272
00:24:25.430 --> 00:24:26.430
So...
所以...


273
00:24:28.010 --> 00:24:29.840
How does it feel to be a goddess?
成为女神的感觉如何？


274
00:24:32.450 --> 00:24:35.620
Well, I'm not a goddess yet.
好吧, 我还不是女神


275
00:24:36.890 --> 00:24:38.060
Just Sienna.
只是沙织


276
00:24:38.080 --> 00:24:40.880
But her Cosmo is getting stronger by the day,
但她的小宇宙一天比一天强大


277
00:24:40.960 --> 00:24:43.550
and someday soon I will become Athena.
不久之后, 我将成为雅典娜


278
00:24:48.510 --> 00:24:50.680
Most people would be excited
大多数人会感到兴奋


279
00:24:51.440 --> 00:24:53.460
to have breakfast with a future goddess.
与未来的女神共进早餐


280
00:24:56.420 --> 00:24:57.840
Guess I'm not most people, then.
看来我不是大多数人


281
00:24:59.480 --> 00:25:01.230
Well, then maybe you should...
那么, 也许你应该...


282
00:25:04.900 --> 00:25:06.320
Maybe I should what?
也许我应该什么？


283
00:25:13.790 --> 00:25:15.080
You should back off.
你应该退后


284
00:25:15.790 --> 00:25:17.080
Jeez, don't be so sensitive.
哎呀, 别这么敏感嘛


285
00:25:19.250 --> 00:25:20.540
Just get away from me, okay?
离我远点, 好吗？


286
00:25:20.630 --> 00:25:22.170
- Okay, I'm sorry. - Just get away...
- 好吧, 对不起 - 走开...


287
00:25:30.890 --> 00:25:31.720
Hey!
嘿！


288
00:25:33.760 --> 00:25:35.220
Dad!
爸爸


289
00:25:35.770 --> 00:25:36.640
Hey!
嘿！


290
00:25:37.270 --> 00:25:39.230
- Are you okay? - Wait!
- 你还好吗？ - 等等


291
00:25:43.070 --> 00:25:44.440
What's going on?
怎么了？


292
00:25:45.110 --> 00:25:46.820
She could kill you right now.
她现在就能杀了你


293
00:25:47.320 --> 00:25:49.490
I'm here, sweetheart, just relax.
我在这里, 亲爱的, 放轻松


294
00:25:57.790 --> 00:25:58.910
What just happened?
刚才发生了什么？


295
00:26:03.540 --> 00:26:06.550
She bears a goddess's Cosmo in the body of a mortal.
她以凡人之躯承载着一个女神的小宇宙


296
00:26:13.430 --> 00:26:17.220
When our sensors detect a potential Cosmo burst,
当我们的传感器检测到潜在的小宇宙爆发时


297
00:26:17.930 --> 00:26:20.600
the building automatically blocks the signal.
建筑物就会自动屏蔽信号


298
00:26:21.690 --> 00:26:24.940
It's the only way we can keep Sienna hidden from Guraad.
只有这样才能不让古拉杜发现沙织


299
00:26:25.220 --> 00:26:28.060
Which is why I am stuck here like a prisoner.
这就是我像囚犯一样被困在这里的原因


300
00:26:32.070 --> 00:26:33.080
Excuse me.
打扰一下


301
00:26:34.550 --> 00:26:37.340
Wait. Wait, so... So you really are...?
等等, 那么...你真的是...


302
00:26:48.300 --> 00:26:50.840
You really think this guy could beat the Pegasus Knight?
你真的认为这家伙能打败天马座圣斗士？


303
00:26:51.470 --> 00:26:54.090
Perhaps. If we give him the prototype.
也许吧 如果我们给他一套暗黑圣衣的话


304
00:27:07.650 --> 00:27:09.150
Next candidate?
下一个候选人？


305
00:27:13.660 --> 00:27:14.660
You giving up already?
你已经放弃了？


306
00:27:25.580 --> 00:27:27.380
What the hell are you made of?
你到底是什么做的？


307
00:27:28.800 --> 00:27:29.760
Disengage.
别打了


308
00:27:34.330 --> 00:27:35.790
We ain't done yet.
我们还没完呢


309
00:27:41.480 --> 00:27:43.810
You made your point, Cassios.
你说得很清楚, 卡西欧士


310
00:27:43.870 --> 00:27:45.170
You're a strong man.
你是个坚强的人


311
00:27:45.900 --> 00:27:48.230
But you're just a man.
但你只是个人


312
00:27:53.400 --> 00:27:54.700
I have a problem.
我有个麻烦


313
00:27:55.240 --> 00:27:56.950
You met him in your ring.
你在你的擂台上见过他


314
00:27:57.470 --> 00:27:58.310
The kid.
那个孩子


315
00:27:58.430 --> 00:28:00.260
His power's a liability.
他的力量是个负担


316
00:28:00.760 --> 00:28:04.550
Once he learns to control it, no living man will be able to stop him.
一旦他学会控制它, 任何活人都无法阻止他


317
00:28:05.750 --> 00:28:07.710
What, you think I could, though?
怎么, 你觉得我可以吗？


318
00:28:08.290 --> 00:28:10.630
You know, with your prototype thing?
穿上你那暗黑圣衣？


319
00:28:11.500 --> 00:28:12.500
I have a good ear.
我的耳朵很灵


320
00:28:13.590 --> 00:28:14.930
So, what's your price?
那么, 你想要多少钱？


321
00:28:17.330 --> 00:28:18.590
Well, that depends.
那要看情况了


322
00:28:19.860 --> 00:28:21.030
Can I kill him?
我能杀了他吗？


323
00:28:21.060 --> 00:28:22.720
That's kind of the point.
这才是重点


324
00:28:23.730 --> 00:28:25.170
I'll do it for free.
我免费帮你


325
00:28:51.040 --> 00:28:53.340
- You all right? - I'm better.
- 你还好吗？ - 我好多了


326
00:28:54.510 --> 00:28:57.430
- You? - I'm good. I guess.
- 你呢？ - 我很好 我想


327
00:28:59.300 --> 00:29:01.970
It's just that I can't believe you really are a...
只是我不敢相信你真的是一个...


328
00:29:02.060 --> 00:29:03.060
A goddess?
女神？


329
00:29:05.180 --> 00:29:06.980
I'm never gonna call you that.
我永远不会那样叫你的


330
00:29:07.370 --> 00:29:09.080
That's fine with me.
我没意见


331
00:29:10.060 --> 00:29:13.860
So how do people usually react when they learn you're Athena?
那么, 当人们知道你是雅典娜时, 通常会有什么反应呢？


332
00:29:14.970 --> 00:29:15.810
Varies.
各不相同


333
00:29:16.610 --> 00:29:19.530
Like, the day after I was born, someone tried to kill me.
比如, 我出生的第二天, 就有人想杀我


334
00:29:19.710 --> 00:29:20.720
No.
不


335
00:29:22.490 --> 00:29:25.620
Not even you could annoy someone that much in just one day.
即使是你, 也不可能在一天之内就那样惹恼一个人


336
00:29:26.540 --> 00:29:29.830
I was told a knight in gold armor gave his life to save mine.
他们告诉我, 一位穿着黄金圣衣的圣斗士为救我献出了生命


337
00:29:31.290 --> 00:29:33.830
When they found him, he was still holding me in his arms.
当他们找到他时, 他还抱着我


338
00:29:33.920 --> 00:29:35.920
Who found you? Alman?
谁找到你的？光政？


339
00:29:36.840 --> 00:29:37.840
And Guraad.
还有古拉杜


340
00:29:40.380 --> 00:29:42.880
Though she was a little more into the gold armor.
虽然她更喜欢黄金圣衣


341
00:29:43.930 --> 00:29:47.560
Used it to develop technology far beyond anything you could imagine.
利用它开发出来的技术远远超出你的想象


342
00:29:48.790 --> 00:29:49.830
Look at the bright side.
往好的方面看


343
00:29:51.220 --> 00:29:53.260
Half your foster family is great.
你的寄养家庭至少有一半还不错


344
00:29:54.360 --> 00:29:56.990
When Alman's around you, he almost looks like a real dad.
当光政在你身边时, 他几乎就像一个真正的父亲


345
00:29:58.450 --> 00:30:01.700
Alman is my dad, and I love him more than anything in the world.
光政就是我的父亲, 我爱他胜过世界上的一切


346
00:30:03.360 --> 00:30:07.240
Although that might be hard for you to understand, street boy.
虽然你可能很难理解, 街头小子


347
00:30:08.750 --> 00:30:09.750
I do.
我能理解


348
00:30:12.820 --> 00:30:14.650
I had someone like that once.
我曾经也有过这样的亲人


349
00:30:16.340 --> 00:30:17.340
Your sister?
你姐姐？


350
00:30:20.050 --> 00:30:21.300
What was she like?
她是个什么样的人？


351
00:30:23.310 --> 00:30:24.770
She was kind.
她很善良


352
00:30:26.950 --> 00:30:28.160
<i>And strong.</i>
<i>也很强大</i>


353
00:30:29.390 --> 00:30:31.940
And protected me when I couldn't protect myself.
在我还不能保护自己的时候保护着我


354
00:30:33.460 --> 00:30:35.420
And you won't stop until you find her.
不找到她, 你是不会罢休的


355
00:30:35.900 --> 00:30:38.860
You really don't care that I've become your bodyguard, do you?
你真的不在乎我当不当你的保镖，是吗？


356
00:30:39.460 --> 00:30:41.670
I will someday become Athena.
总有一天, 我会成为雅典娜


357
00:30:42.200 --> 00:30:43.620
I don't have a choice.
我别无选择


358
00:30:43.700 --> 00:30:46.370
But that doesn't mean you have to become the Pegasus Knight.
但这并不意味着你必须成为天马座圣斗士


359
00:30:46.400 --> 00:30:48.070
Alman said it's my destiny.
光政说这是我的命运


360
00:30:48.500 --> 00:30:50.500
Nobody's destiny is written in stone.
没有人的命运是一成不变的


361
00:30:51.770 --> 00:30:52.860
Except yours.
除了你的


362
00:30:54.330 --> 00:30:56.170
Your Cosmo bursts,
你的小宇宙爆发时


363
00:30:56.260 --> 00:30:58.010
do they come with visions?
会有幻象出现吗？


364
00:30:58.710 --> 00:31:00.050
You have visions too?
你也有幻象？


365
00:31:00.130 --> 00:31:01.300
What does it matter?
这有什么意义吗？


366
00:31:01.400 --> 00:31:05.570
Cosmo visions are a window into the universe.
小宇宙幻象是一扇通往宇宙的窗户


367
00:31:06.930 --> 00:31:08.540
They can show us things.
可以向我们展示一些事情


368
00:31:11.520 --> 00:31:14.190
So that Silver Knight your dad mentioned...?
你爸爸提到的那个白银圣斗士....？


369
00:31:14.270 --> 00:31:15.900
- Who, Marin? - Marin.
- 谁, 魔铃？ - 魔铃


370
00:31:15.980 --> 00:31:18.530
Do you think if he could teach me to control my Cosmo,
你觉得如果他能教我控制我的小宇宙的话


371
00:31:18.560 --> 00:31:20.320
I could use it to find my sister?
我可以用它找到我姐姐吗？


372
00:31:21.430 --> 00:31:22.470
Maybe.
也许吧


373
00:31:24.410 --> 00:31:25.620
If that's what you want.
如果这就是你想要的


374
00:32:00.650 --> 00:32:02.950
He's drained of Cosmo, Guraad.
他的小宇宙被吸干了, 古拉杜


375
00:32:06.250 --> 00:32:07.790
Won't get another dose.
不用再来一轮了


376
00:32:10.070 --> 00:32:12.610
The prototype procedure has started.
暗黑圣衣程序已启动


377
00:32:13.080 --> 00:32:14.580
It'll be ready tomorrow.
明天就好了


378
00:32:15.290 --> 00:32:16.380
Any issues?
有问题吗？


379
00:32:17.000 --> 00:32:18.000
Just one.
只有一个


380
00:32:19.090 --> 00:32:20.420
Why Cassios?
为什么是卡西欧士？


381
00:32:21.050 --> 00:32:22.460
'Cause you failed.
因为你失败了


382
00:32:24.640 --> 00:32:28.100
You know, the target was assisted by Alman Kido.
要知道, 目标有城户光政的协助


383
00:32:28.210 --> 00:32:30.170
A personal bad penny.
私人旧债


384
00:32:31.890 --> 00:32:33.730
Athena's growing stronger by the day,
雅典娜越来越强大了


385
00:32:33.820 --> 00:32:36.660
and now she'll have the Pegasus Knight by her side.
现在, 她将由天马座圣斗士守护着


386
00:32:36.730 --> 00:32:40.730
I reckon the boy's got some Cosmo. Doesn't mean he's a knight yet.
我觉得这孩子是有点小宇宙了 并不意味着他已经是圣斗士了


387
00:32:40.940 --> 00:32:42.740
I don't need cold comfort, Nero.
我不需要冷冰冰的安慰, 尼禄


388
00:32:42.860 --> 00:32:45.530
I need to know where on Earth Alman is hiding the girl.
我要知道光政到底把那女孩藏在哪儿了


389
00:32:45.620 --> 00:32:48.170
So we can neutralize her before she becomes Athena
这样我们就能在她变成雅典娜并毁灭世界之前


390
00:32:48.200 --> 00:32:49.570
and destroys the world.
解除她的威胁


391
00:32:51.160 --> 00:32:52.200
Beats me.
难住我了


392
00:32:54.120 --> 00:32:56.080
But you could always ask our prisoner.
不过, 你可以问问我们的囚犯


393
00:32:59.130 --> 00:33:00.500
We have a prisoner?
我们抓了一个囚犯？


394
00:33:36.650 --> 00:33:37.480
Hey!
嘿！


395
00:33:38.540 --> 00:33:39.670
Hey, wait up.
嘿, 等等


396
00:33:40.420 --> 00:33:41.460
Yeah?
怎么了？


397
00:33:42.710 --> 00:33:46.510
I...I just figured you could focus more on your training if you weren't
我只是在想, 你应该可以更专注于你的训练


398
00:33:46.590 --> 00:33:49.090
worried about where your next meal was coming from.
如果不用担心下一顿饭从哪里来的话


399
00:33:51.130 --> 00:33:52.040
Thanks.
谢谢


400
00:33:59.650 --> 00:34:00.780
Thank you.
谢谢


401
00:34:01.920 --> 00:34:02.860
I guess.
我猜也是


402
00:34:05.780 --> 00:34:06.780
Seiya!
星矢


403
00:34:07.790 --> 00:34:08.910
Time to go.
该走了


404
00:34:11.660 --> 00:34:12.660
See you.
再见


405
00:34:15.870 --> 00:34:16.870
Take a seat.
请坐


406
00:34:21.730 --> 00:34:23.560
Don't get any big ideas.
不要想法太多


407
00:34:24.340 --> 00:34:27.710
Goddesses don't have boyfriends.
女神不会有男朋友的


408
00:34:27.800 --> 00:34:29.680
- How many dads does Sienna have? - Buckle up.
- 沙织小姐这是有几个爸爸啊？ - 系好安全带


409
00:34:40.040 --> 00:34:41.050
Lunchbox?
午餐盒？


410
00:34:42.900 --> 00:34:44.610
That's unusually kind of you.
你这是太好了啊


411
00:34:46.900 --> 00:34:49.070
I just thought he might as well enjoy his last meal,
我只是想让他好好享受最后一餐


412
00:34:49.150 --> 00:34:51.360
since Marin's probably gonna kill him anyway.
因为魔铃很可能会杀了他的


413
00:34:52.860 --> 00:34:53.870
Right.
对


414
00:35:16.640 --> 00:35:18.560
So where am I supposed to go?
那我该去哪儿？


415
00:35:25.400 --> 00:35:27.230
Okay. Just drop me off up there.
好 就在那边把我放下来


416
00:35:27.580 --> 00:35:29.080
Not how it works.
不是这样的


417
00:35:47.880 --> 00:35:51.630
"Those who seek the master must do so on foot."
" 千里之行 始于足下"


418
00:36:21.580 --> 00:36:23.500
What the hell am I doing here?
我到底在这里干什么？


419
00:36:24.620 --> 00:36:26.420
I was wondering the same thing.
我也在想同样的问题


420
00:36:39.850 --> 00:36:42.020
You must be Marin.
你一定是魔铃


421
00:36:42.840 --> 00:36:44.970
- The Silver Knight. - You look surprised.
- 白银圣斗士 - 你看起来很惊讶


422
00:36:45.000 --> 00:36:47.290
Yeah. No, I'm... I mean...
是的 不 我...我是说...


423
00:36:48.730 --> 00:36:50.360
No offense, I thought you'd be a man.
无意冒犯, 我以为你是个男人


424
00:36:50.440 --> 00:36:51.810
No offense taken.
没觉得冒犯


425
00:36:51.900 --> 00:36:53.440
I thought the same of you.
我也是这么以为你的


426
00:36:55.100 --> 00:36:57.150
What's the training schedule like here?
这里的训练安排是什么？


427
00:36:57.270 --> 00:36:59.400
I only train knights.
我只训练圣斗士


428
00:37:01.580 --> 00:37:03.500
I'm told I'm the Pegasus Knight.
据说我是天马座圣斗士


429
00:37:05.290 --> 00:37:08.340
You're not the first boy with a pretty necklace to show up here.
你不是第一个带着漂亮项链出现在这里的男孩


430
00:37:09.590 --> 00:37:11.390
Is there a test I can take or something?
有什么测试可以测测吗？


431
00:37:15.840 --> 00:37:17.760
The Pegasus Knight is brave.
天马座圣斗士勇敢


432
00:37:20.930 --> 00:37:21.770
Check.
对


433
00:37:22.310 --> 00:37:23.390
Humble.
谦卑


434
00:37:23.530 --> 00:37:24.700
Check.
对


435
00:37:24.730 --> 00:37:27.820
And committed to protecting Athena with his life.
发誓用生命保护雅典娜


436
00:37:28.740 --> 00:37:32.360
Okay, that's where this whole situation gets a little sticky.
好吧, 这就是情况变得有点棘手的地方


437
00:37:32.440 --> 00:37:33.900
See, I lost my sister... Hey!
你看, 我失去了我的姐姐...嘿


438
00:37:35.320 --> 00:37:36.780
I just got up here!
我才刚上来


439
00:37:38.260 --> 00:37:41.030
I just got up here.
我才刚上来


440
00:37:44.620 --> 00:37:46.090
I'm not going down there.
我不会下去的


441
00:38:17.280 --> 00:38:18.860
There's nothing for you here.
这里没有你要的东西


442
00:38:19.410 --> 00:38:20.940
What are you? Like, a ninja?
你是什么人？忍者吗？


443
00:38:23.950 --> 00:38:26.910
Listen, I only wanna find my sister. Sienna said you could help.
听着 我只想找到我姐姐 沙织小姐说你能帮忙


444
00:38:26.990 --> 00:38:29.450
I knew a knight just like you.
我认识一个和你一样的圣斗士


445
00:38:29.540 --> 00:38:31.460
He desired power for his own goals.
他渴望变强，只是为了实现自己的目标


446
00:38:31.540 --> 00:38:33.540
- Which was? - The Phoenix.
- 哪个？ - 凤凰座


447
00:38:33.630 --> 00:38:35.590
The most powerful of Athena's knights.
雅典娜最强大的圣斗士


448
00:38:35.610 --> 00:38:37.660
You mean, aside from the Pegasus Knight.
你是说, 除了天马座圣斗士之外？


449
00:38:40.260 --> 00:38:42.140
I'll have Mylock come get you in the morning.
我会让晨己明早来接你


450
00:38:42.220 --> 00:38:43.890
No. Come on, I made it this far.
不, 拜托, 我好不容易才到这里的


451
00:38:43.970 --> 00:38:45.310
And how far is that?
有多不容易？


452
00:38:46.000 --> 00:38:47.990
Do you even know how far you need to go?
你知道自己还有多远的路要走吗？


453
00:38:48.640 --> 00:38:50.260
Just give me one chance.
给我一个机会


454
00:38:56.360 --> 00:38:57.860
If you can break this rock...
如果你能打破这块石头...


455
00:38:59.050 --> 00:39:01.180
then you can be my student.
那么你就可以成为我的学生


456
00:39:09.870 --> 00:39:10.870
Fair enough.
很公平


457
00:39:11.850 --> 00:39:13.040
Where's the hammer?
锤子在哪？


458
00:39:15.970 --> 00:39:18.270
Come on, I can't break a rock with my bare hands.
拜托, 我不可能赤手空拳打碎一块石头


459
00:39:18.990 --> 00:39:20.120
A knight could.
圣斗士可以


460
00:39:21.970 --> 00:39:23.340
You can't be serious.
你不是认真的吧


461
00:39:27.330 --> 00:39:28.870
You're serious.
你是认真的


462
00:39:44.020 --> 00:39:45.820
I told you, this was stupid!
我告诉过你, 这样太蠢了！


463
00:39:50.160 --> 00:39:54.000
Your flesh, this rock, the stars in the sky,
你的肉体, 这块岩石, 天上的星辰


464
00:39:54.080 --> 00:39:58.050
all things in the cosmos are made from the same atoms.
宇宙万物都是由相同的原子构成的


465
00:39:58.120 --> 00:40:02.380
From the moment we are born, we all hold a Cosmo within ourselves.
从出生的那一刻起, 我们每个人的体内都有一个小宇宙


466
00:40:02.480 --> 00:40:05.230
A knight can make it explode.
圣斗士可以让其爆发


467
00:40:05.720 --> 00:40:09.730
And shatter the atoms of any object.
并粉碎任何物体的原子


468
00:40:14.690 --> 00:40:16.810
How's that supposed to make any sense?
这怎么能说得通呢？


469
00:40:20.480 --> 00:40:21.490
Focus.
集中注意力


470
00:40:23.320 --> 00:40:24.740
Clear your mind.
理清思绪


471
00:40:25.350 --> 00:40:27.390
Feel the Cosmo within you.
感受你体内的小宇宙


472
00:41:03.150 --> 00:41:04.110
<i>Seiya!</i>
<i>星矢!</i>


473
00:41:08.160 --> 00:41:09.910
This is stupid, it'll never work!
这太愚蠢了, 根本行不通！


474
00:41:09.990 --> 00:41:11.950
Something clouded your focus at the last minute.
在最后关头, 你的注意力被什么东西遮住了


475
00:41:12.040 --> 00:41:14.750
Figures. Guess I'm not the Pegasus Knight after all.
看出来了 估计我终究不是天马座圣斗士


476
00:41:14.830 --> 00:41:16.830
No, you're not.
对, 你不是


477
00:41:17.070 --> 00:41:19.240
But maybe you will be.
但也许你将来会是的


478
00:41:20.340 --> 00:41:22.090
Are you ready to start your training?
你准备好开始训练了吗？


479
00:41:38.940 --> 00:41:41.980
It's a good thing he didn't mind the permanent changes to his body.
好在他并不介意身体的永久性改变


480
00:41:42.070 --> 00:41:44.320
- Well... - What?
- 呃 - 什么？


481
00:41:44.400 --> 00:41:47.400
I might have forgotten to mention the permanent part to him.
我可能忘了跟他说永久性那部分


482
00:41:59.710 --> 00:42:00.880
What the hell is this?
这是什么鬼东西？


483
00:42:00.960 --> 00:42:02.630
What did you do? You made...
你做了什么？你把...


484
00:42:03.300 --> 00:42:05.920
You made me a freaking cyborg!
你把我变成了一个他妈的机器人


485
00:42:16.270 --> 00:42:17.770
What is that?
那是什么？


486
00:42:17.850 --> 00:42:19.350
It's the curse of Athena.
这是雅典娜的诅咒


487
00:42:21.310 --> 00:42:24.230
The war that awaits us is unlike any other before.
等待我们的是一场前所未有的战争


488
00:42:24.780 --> 00:42:27.490
Our enemies are the gods themselves.
我们的敌人就是众神本身


489
00:42:28.700 --> 00:42:30.730
We've all made sacrifices.
我们都做出了牺牲


490
00:42:32.740 --> 00:42:37.330
But what is flesh in comparison to the power to crush the immortals?
但是, 与碾压众神的力量相比, 肉体又算得了什么呢？


491
00:42:42.460 --> 00:42:44.170
A war with the gods, huh?
与众神开战？


492
00:42:44.390 --> 00:42:46.760
There's only one person I wanna crush.
我只想搞死一个人


493
00:42:50.090 --> 00:42:51.800
Well, that was a nice little show.
这真是一场精彩的小演出


494
00:42:51.890 --> 00:42:54.180
Let's move on. We have bigger issues at hand.
先别管他 我们手头还有更大的问题


495
00:42:54.260 --> 00:42:56.220
- Bigger than his ego? - Your prisoner.
- 比他的自负还大？ - 你的囚犯


496
00:42:56.300 --> 00:42:58.360
He's a tough one. I can't get him to talk.
他是个硬骨头 我没法让他开口


497
00:42:58.620 --> 00:43:01.460
- Any ideas? - Have you tried asking nicely?
- 有什么主意吗？ - 你试过友好一点地询问吗？


498
00:43:09.150 --> 00:43:10.770
Let's get a baseline.
我们来摸下底


499
00:43:22.370 --> 00:43:24.080
Show me what you know.
让我看看你有什么本事


500
00:43:24.170 --> 00:43:26.590
You mean, fight you? Now?
你是说, 跟你打一架？现在？


501
00:43:33.070 --> 00:43:34.820
You came here to train, yes?
你是来受训的, 是吗？


502
00:43:39.870 --> 00:43:42.120
Is dancing all you can do?
你只会跳舞吗？


503
00:44:11.550 --> 00:44:13.340
Shouldn't I have a weapon or something?
我是不是应该有个武器什么的？


504
00:44:13.360 --> 00:44:15.200
Athena's knights wield no weapon.
雅典娜的圣斗士们从不拿武器


505
00:44:15.760 --> 00:44:16.800
That sucks.
真菜


506
00:44:45.580 --> 00:44:46.960
Okay, I felt that one.
好吧, 我体会到了


507
00:44:47.130 --> 00:44:48.800
It wasn't a direct hit.
又没有直接击中你


508
00:44:56.090 --> 00:44:57.590
How the hell'd you do that?
你是怎么做到的？


509
00:44:57.680 --> 00:44:59.300
You want a weapon?
你想要武器吗？


510
00:44:59.450 --> 00:45:01.450
Your Cosmo is your weapon.
你的小宇宙就是你的武器


511
00:45:01.650 --> 00:45:03.270
Focus your energy,
集中精力


512
00:45:03.350 --> 00:45:05.480
let it burn inside of you.
让它在你体内燃烧


513
00:45:05.560 --> 00:45:07.440
Release it all at once.
一次性全部释放


514
00:45:07.520 --> 00:45:08.760
Like a shooting star.
就像一颗流星


515
00:45:09.480 --> 00:45:11.400
Felt more like a meteor shower to me.
我感觉更像是一场流星雨


516
00:45:17.260 --> 00:45:19.780
So do I get to learn this meteor fist of yours?
那我能学学你这套流星拳吗？


517
00:45:20.090 --> 00:45:21.090
You must...
必然的...


518
00:45:21.460 --> 00:45:24.170
if you want to survive the battles that await you.
如果你想在等待着你的战斗中幸存的话


519
00:46:31.650 --> 00:46:32.650
Sienna!
沙织


520
00:46:37.400 --> 00:46:38.950
It's all right. It's all right.
没事了 没事的


521
00:46:39.030 --> 00:46:40.610
It's all right. It's all right.
没事了 没事的


522
00:46:40.700 --> 00:46:42.320
I'm here. It's all right.
我在这 没事了


523
00:46:44.740 --> 00:46:47.620
I had another vision. Bad one.
我又看到了一个幻象 很糟糕


524
00:46:48.870 --> 00:46:50.330
It's okay, it's all gone now.
没关系, 现在都过去了


525
00:46:51.020 --> 00:46:51.850
Dad...
爸爸...


526
00:46:53.630 --> 00:46:56.380
How can you be so sure I'll grow up to protect the world?
你怎么能确定我长大后能保护这个世界？


527
00:46:56.410 --> 00:46:58.790
You are the goddess of wisdom, remember?
你是智慧女神, 还记得吗？


528
00:46:58.920 --> 00:47:00.230
And warfare.
还有战争女神


529
00:47:01.800 --> 00:47:03.300
And you're my baby girl.
你是我的宝贝女儿


530
00:47:03.990 --> 00:47:06.330
The most loving and stubborn.
最有爱心, 也最固执


531
00:47:06.390 --> 00:47:09.100
Nothing could stop you from doing what's right.
没有什么能阻止你做正确的事


532
00:47:09.500 --> 00:47:10.960
What did you see?
你看到了什么？


533
00:47:12.960 --> 00:47:15.170
People... burning.
人....在燃烧


534
00:47:15.520 --> 00:47:17.280
Cities in ruins.
废墟中的城市


535
00:47:17.900 --> 00:47:19.360
Everything...
一切...


536
00:47:20.530 --> 00:47:21.820
destroyed.
都被摧毁了


537
00:47:21.910 --> 00:47:23.910
We won't let that happen, will we?
我们不会让这种事情发生的, 不是吗？


538
00:47:23.990 --> 00:47:26.120
You don't understand. It was Athena.
你不明白 是雅典娜干的


539
00:47:26.200 --> 00:47:27.790
She was doing it. I...
她正在动手 我...


540
00:47:29.080 --> 00:47:30.290
I was doing it.
我正在动手


541
00:47:31.400 --> 00:47:34.590
Visions are just... possibilities.
幻象只是...一种可能


542
00:47:34.780 --> 00:47:37.620
Dad, I know you'd let the world burn to keep me safe...
爸爸 我知道你宁愿让世界毁灭 也要保护我的安全....


543
00:47:39.330 --> 00:47:41.580
but what if that's not me anymore?
但如果那个人不再是我了呢？


544
00:47:56.060 --> 00:47:58.280
Prove to me you're worthy. Focus.
向我证明你的价值 集中注意力


545
00:48:02.740 --> 00:48:03.950
Is that all you've got?
你就这点本事？


546
00:48:06.210 --> 00:48:07.340
Your body is here.
你的身体在这里


547
00:48:08.440 --> 00:48:10.100
But your mind is elsewhere.
但你心思在别的地方


548
00:48:18.470 --> 00:48:19.430
<i>Seiya.</i>
<i>星矢</i>


549
00:48:19.750 --> 00:48:21.790
There's so many things I need to tell you.
我有很多事情要告诉你


550
00:48:21.900 --> 00:48:23.570
I'm here to protect you.
我是来保护你的


551
00:48:25.250 --> 00:48:26.670
Now stop my attack.
现在阻止我的攻击


552
00:48:35.690 --> 00:48:36.940
You're failing.
你失败了


553
00:48:40.690 --> 00:48:42.110
Was he a knight too?
他也是圣斗士吗？


554
00:48:42.250 --> 00:48:43.620
The Pegasus?
天马座？


555
00:48:44.110 --> 00:48:47.700
Mind and body must become one.
身心必须合一


556
00:48:51.430 --> 00:48:54.150
A knight's power comes from within.
圣斗士的力量来自内心


557
00:49:05.100 --> 00:49:06.560
You give up?
你投降了？


558
00:49:10.470 --> 00:49:13.270
If you can't do this, you'll never be a knight.
如果你做不到这一点, 就永远当不了圣斗士


559
00:49:24.900 --> 00:49:25.900
You give up?
你投降了？


560
00:50:11.110 --> 00:50:13.050
How did you say you ended up here, again?
你说你是怎么到这里来的？


561
00:50:13.890 --> 00:50:15.890
I didn't say. And it's none of your...
我没说 这不关你的...


562
00:50:15.910 --> 00:50:18.040
Right, I'm not supposed to know. I know.
对 我不应该知道 我知道


563
00:50:20.210 --> 00:50:23.250
My destiny is bound to this island.
我的命运与这座小岛紧紧相连


564
00:50:24.090 --> 00:50:26.130
Well, that sounds like a lonely existence.
这听起来像是一种孤独的生活


565
00:50:26.370 --> 00:50:28.080
But not one without purpose.
但也不是毫无使命的


566
00:50:28.520 --> 00:50:29.660
You know, I...
你知道, 我...


567
00:50:30.590 --> 00:50:32.180
I have a purpose too.
我也有自己的使命


568
00:50:32.260 --> 00:50:33.810
To find my sister.
找到我姐姐


569
00:50:34.010 --> 00:50:37.390
A knight should not mistake obsession for purpose.
圣斗士不应将痴迷误当成使命


570
00:50:38.090 --> 00:50:40.130
I know there is pain in your past...
我知道你的过去很痛苦...


571
00:50:40.770 --> 00:50:43.940
but beyond that pain, there lies your strength.
但在痛苦之外, 还有你的力量


572
00:50:44.670 --> 00:50:47.930
Find it and the armor will accept you.
找到了, 圣衣就会接受你


573
00:50:48.820 --> 00:50:50.820
This is what your sister would've wanted.
这是你姐姐想要的


574
00:50:52.820 --> 00:50:53.990
Get some sleep.
好好睡一觉


575
00:52:44.950 --> 00:52:46.530
I get it.
我明白了


576
00:52:46.620 --> 00:52:48.450
You're tough.
你很强悍


577
00:52:49.120 --> 00:52:53.120
You know, someone once taught me
有人曾经教过我


578
00:52:53.240 --> 00:52:56.110
that all men, no matter how tough,
所有男人, 无论多么强悍


579
00:52:57.320 --> 00:52:58.900
have something they fear.
都有他们害怕的东西


580
00:53:06.320 --> 00:53:09.700
I wonder what it is a big man like you fears the most.
我很想知道像你这样的大块头最害怕什么


581
00:53:28.770 --> 00:53:30.190
Who are you?
你是谁？


582
00:53:35.320 --> 00:53:38.120
You have no idea what I'm capable of.
你根本不知道我的能耐


583
00:53:40.370 --> 00:53:42.350
Make it stop.
让它停下来


584
00:53:46.290 --> 00:53:47.460
Make it stop!
让它停下来！


585
00:53:47.970 --> 00:53:49.310
Make it go away.
让它消失


586
00:53:50.750 --> 00:53:51.590
Now...
现在...


587
00:53:52.840 --> 00:53:56.090
would you mind telling me where I can find Alman Kido?
你能告诉我在哪里可以找到城户光政吗？


588
00:53:57.340 --> 00:53:58.720
Make it stop!
让它停下来！


589
00:54:05.310 --> 00:54:09.060
- This one's bigger than the last one. - And your Cosmo is stronger.
- 这个比上个大啊 - 你的小宇宙也更强了


590
00:54:09.180 --> 00:54:11.140
Now, show me what you've learned.
现在, 让我看看你学到了点什么


591
00:55:39.070 --> 00:55:40.150
You did it, Seiya.
你做到了, 星矢


592
00:55:41.410 --> 00:55:43.200
The Pegasus armor is...
天马座圣衣是...


593
00:55:56.860 --> 00:56:00.080
You can't use it. Only the Pegasus can.
你用不了的 只有天马座才可以


594
00:56:00.170 --> 00:56:02.090
That's why you're coming with us.
这就是为什么你要跟我们走


595
00:56:13.190 --> 00:56:14.020
Alman.
光政


596
00:56:15.480 --> 00:56:16.860
He was a part of it.
他也参与了


597
00:56:18.320 --> 00:56:21.650
He was there when Guraad took Patricia.
古拉杜抓走星华的时候, 他也在场


598
00:56:26.310 --> 00:56:27.980
I want off this island.
我要离开这个岛


599
00:56:30.790 --> 00:56:32.040
You are not ready.
你还没准备好


600
00:56:32.120 --> 00:56:34.040
Your training is not over.
你的训练还没有结束


601
00:56:35.470 --> 00:56:36.640
It is now.
现在结束了


602
00:56:47.350 --> 00:56:49.470
Alman's been playing me for a fool!
光政把我当傻瓜耍


603
00:56:49.560 --> 00:56:51.100
You must calm down.
你必须冷静下来


604
00:56:51.180 --> 00:56:54.230
If your heart and mind aren't clear, the armor will reject you.
如果你的心智不清晰, 圣衣就会拒绝你


605
00:56:54.310 --> 00:56:55.810
To hell with the armor!
让圣衣见鬼去吧


606
00:57:26.970 --> 00:57:27.970
Seiya.
星矢


607
00:57:29.220 --> 00:57:30.430
I don't care.
我不在乎


608
00:57:32.060 --> 00:57:33.770
You can either kill me now...
你要么现在就杀了我...


609
00:57:36.650 --> 00:57:37.940
or send me back.
要么就把我送回去


610
00:57:44.240 --> 00:57:46.070
Let's go. One more round, guys.
我们走 再来一轮 伙计们


611
00:57:47.110 --> 00:57:48.120
Come on.
来吧


612
00:57:55.830 --> 00:57:57.170
How's it coming along?
进展如何？


613
00:58:00.100 --> 00:58:02.400
You want this to work, I need more time.
要想成功, 我需要更多时间


614
00:58:04.260 --> 00:58:05.920
Be careful, you idiot!
小心点, 笨蛋


615
00:58:11.390 --> 00:58:15.480
Yeah, running out of sparring partners. You care to join?
呃 没有陪练了 你想加入吗？


616
00:58:15.570 --> 00:58:17.440
Oh, I'm sorry. Busy day.
哦 对不起 太忙了


617
00:58:19.000 --> 00:58:23.550
Right, right. You're playing with your god-killing toy over here.
对 对 你在这玩你的弑神玩具呢


618
00:58:24.940 --> 00:58:25.940
Yeah.
呃


619
00:58:27.380 --> 00:58:29.680
So much trouble for one little girl.
一个小姑娘还用得着这么麻烦


620
00:58:29.740 --> 00:58:31.370
You know, if you ask me,
要我说


621
00:58:31.450 --> 00:58:35.080
I'd be more than happy to snap her neck the old-fashioned way.
我很乐意用老办法扭断她的脖子


622
00:58:37.270 --> 00:58:42.190
Any damage to Sienna's body might awaken Athena's Cosmo within her.
沙织身体的任何损伤 都可能会唤醒她体内雅典娜的小宇宙


623
00:58:42.410 --> 00:58:45.080
Yeah, I don't even know what that means.
是啊, 我都不知道那是什么意思


624
00:58:45.630 --> 00:58:49.680
It means you can't dismantle a nuclear bomb by smashing it with a club.
意思就是 你拿棍棒敲两下就想拆除核弹 那是不可能的


625
00:58:50.930 --> 00:58:52.390
I'd sure love to try.
我很想试试


626
00:58:53.740 --> 00:58:55.110
It's not happening.
别做梦了


627
00:58:56.600 --> 00:58:57.730
Make it work.
赶紧搞定


628
00:59:06.490 --> 00:59:07.650
Alman!
光政


629
00:59:07.740 --> 00:59:09.190
I know what you did!
我知道你干过什么！


630
00:59:10.030 --> 00:59:12.950
- Come face me, you coward. - Stand down!
- 出来对质, 你个懦夫 - 退后


631
00:59:13.900 --> 00:59:15.200
I'll handle this.
我来处理


632
00:59:15.740 --> 00:59:17.580
- Seiya, please. - Alman!
- 星矢, 别 - 光政


633
00:59:18.290 --> 00:59:19.490
Please calm down.
请冷静


634
00:59:19.510 --> 00:59:20.720
Stand back!
退后


635
00:59:21.910 --> 00:59:23.490
You can't hide from me.
你躲不了的


636
00:59:24.510 --> 00:59:25.510
Seiya!
星矢


637
00:59:25.840 --> 00:59:28.590
He took Patricia. He was in on it.
他带走了星华 他也参与了


638
00:59:28.670 --> 00:59:30.110
There's more to it than that.
不止如此


639
00:59:30.180 --> 00:59:32.640
No! No, you don't wanna do that.
不, 不, 你不会想这么做的


640
00:59:32.720 --> 00:59:34.220
You don't understand.
你不明白


641
00:59:35.090 --> 00:59:37.880
Come with me. I'll tell you what really happened to your sister.
跟我来 我会告诉你你姐姐到底发生了什么事


642
00:59:43.650 --> 00:59:45.270
Sienna, you know the rules.
沙织小姐 你知道规矩的


643
00:59:46.610 --> 00:59:50.740
You must not leave the mansion grounds.
你绝不能离开宅邸


644
01:00:23.450 --> 01:00:24.740
You said you have answers.
你说你有答案


645
01:00:25.310 --> 01:00:26.150
Hey!
嘿！


646
01:00:28.110 --> 01:00:30.740
Alman was there when Guraad took Patricia. He was a part of it.
古拉杜抓走星华时 光政也在场 他也参与了


647
01:00:31.020 --> 01:00:32.380
Tell me I'm wrong.
告诉我我错了


648
01:00:32.900 --> 01:00:34.780
He did it because of me.
他是因为我才这么做的


649
01:00:39.280 --> 01:00:42.070
When I was younger, I had no control at all.
我还小的时候, 根本无法控制自己


650
01:00:42.160 --> 01:00:45.420
One night, my mom was holding me and I had a burst of Cosmo.
一天晚上, 妈妈抱着我, 我的小宇宙突然爆发了


651
01:00:45.720 --> 01:00:47.020
I don't even know how it happened.
我甚至不知道这是怎么发生的


652
01:00:47.040 --> 01:00:51.010
All I remember is she was holding me and I destroyed her arms.
我只记得当时她抱着我, 而我毁了她的手臂


653
01:00:51.180 --> 01:00:53.970
And the next moment, she was dying and it was all my fault.
下一秒, 她就奄奄一息, 而这一切都是我的错


654
01:00:54.330 --> 01:00:56.640
Alman used the power of the gold armor to save her,
光政用黄金圣衣的力量救了她


655
01:00:56.720 --> 01:01:00.020
but ever since the accident, Guraad needs Cosmo to stay alive.
但自从事故发生后, 古拉杜就需要靠小宇宙来维持生命


656
01:01:00.100 --> 01:01:02.180
So what? You've got plenty of it.
那又怎样？你不是有很多


657
01:01:02.620 --> 01:01:04.980
Athena's Cosmo's too powerful. It would kill her.
雅典娜的小宇宙力量太强大了 会杀了她的


658
01:01:05.250 --> 01:01:07.970
That's why she sought out kids like your sister.
这就是为什么她要抓像你姐姐这样的孩子


659
01:01:08.390 --> 01:01:09.810
What did she do to Pat?
她对星华做了什么？


660
01:01:09.830 --> 01:01:11.880
Your sister didn't have any Cosmo.
你姐姐没有小宇宙


661
01:01:11.900 --> 01:01:14.360
Once Guraad figured that out, she let her go.
古拉杜明白这一点后, 就放她走了


662
01:01:15.020 --> 01:01:16.780
But she sent her men to watch her.
但她派人监视着她


663
01:01:17.130 --> 01:01:19.470
Guraad knew Patricia was hiding something.
古拉杜知道星华隐瞒着什么


664
01:01:20.370 --> 01:01:21.370
Me.
我


665
01:01:23.710 --> 01:01:25.540
That's why she never came back.
这就是为什么她再也没有回来


666
01:01:25.750 --> 01:01:28.710
Look, I'm sorry, Seiya. If I knew, I...
对不起 星矢 如果我知道 我...


667
01:01:33.590 --> 01:01:35.590
My mother was never the same after the incident.
事件发生后, 我的母亲完全变了一个人


668
01:01:35.680 --> 01:01:39.930
She became convinced that Athena had returned to this world to end it.
她开始相信雅典娜重生就是为了结束这个世界


669
01:01:40.830 --> 01:01:43.460
She was gonna kill me, so my father forced me into hiding.
她要杀了我, 所以我父亲只好带着我躲起来


670
01:01:43.560 --> 01:01:45.070
And left Pat behind.
抛弃了星华


671
01:01:47.020 --> 01:01:48.940
Your sister wasn't the only one.
你姐姐不是唯一一个


672
01:01:50.860 --> 01:01:52.320
We left them all behind.
被我们抛弃的


673
01:01:55.110 --> 01:01:56.820
How many kids did your family take?
你家劫走了多少孩子？


674
01:02:04.580 --> 01:02:06.920
Our radar picked up Guraad's signature.
我们的雷达发现了古拉杜的踪迹


675
01:02:11.170 --> 01:02:12.670
So it is happening.
终于来了


676
01:02:13.260 --> 01:02:14.970
We don't stand a chance.
我们没有胜算的


677
01:02:15.180 --> 01:02:19.550
You need to get out of here. I'll buy you as much time as I can.
你必须离开这里 我会尽可能多争取点时间


678
01:02:19.640 --> 01:02:21.350
I'm not running from a fight.
我不会逃避战斗


679
01:02:22.080 --> 01:02:23.580
Find Sienna.
找到沙织小姐


680
01:02:24.390 --> 01:02:25.390
Protect her.
保护她


681
01:02:26.480 --> 01:02:28.600
You're the only one I can trust.
你是我唯一可以信任的人


682
01:02:36.170 --> 01:02:37.380
And, Mylock?
晨己


683
01:02:38.950 --> 01:02:40.620
You've been a good friend.
你一直是个好朋友


684
01:02:42.870 --> 01:02:43.870
Thank you.
谢谢


685
01:02:51.340 --> 01:02:54.300
After Pat was taken, I ran away.
星华被抓走后, 我就跑了


686
01:02:55.460 --> 01:02:58.260
All these years, I've never stopped looking for her.
这些年来, 我从未停止过寻找她


687
01:03:00.340 --> 01:03:02.850
Turns out she was the one who was keeping away from me.
原来是她在躲着我


688
01:03:03.510 --> 01:03:05.100
Your sister sacrificed herself
你姐姐牺牲自己


689
01:03:05.170 --> 01:03:07.010
because she believed in what you really are.
因为她相信你的天命所归


690
01:03:07.070 --> 01:03:08.780
I never asked to be a knight.
我从没想过要成为圣斗士


691
01:03:11.400 --> 01:03:13.150
I only wanted to be with Pat.
我只想和星华在一起


692
01:03:14.820 --> 01:03:16.860
You think I wanted any of this?
你以为我想要这些吗？


693
01:03:18.490 --> 01:03:22.160
Sometimes I feel like I'm a guest in my own body.
有时候, 我觉得我就像是自己身体里的客人


694
01:03:24.120 --> 01:03:26.620
In time, I thought I'd learn to control it.
假以时日, 我一定会学会控制它


695
01:03:27.540 --> 01:03:28.960
But you're fighting it.
但你还在努力


696
01:03:31.920 --> 01:03:33.590
What if my mother was right?
如果我母亲是对的呢？


697
01:03:37.630 --> 01:03:42.050
What if I was only born to bring ruin and misery into this world?
如果我的出生只是为了给这个世界带来毁灭和痛苦呢？


698
01:03:42.490 --> 01:03:44.280
That's not who you are.
你不是这样的人


699
01:03:47.520 --> 01:03:48.600
How do you know?
你怎么知道？


700
01:03:50.940 --> 01:03:52.600
I guess I just know.
我想我就是知道


701
01:04:00.030 --> 01:04:01.660
I need you to promise me...
我需要你答应我...


702
01:04:02.570 --> 01:04:04.110
if things go wrong...
如果出了差错...


703
01:04:04.910 --> 01:04:08.620
if, in the end, I become a goddess of war and I can't control my powers...
如果最后我成为了战争女神, 却无法控制自己的力量....


704
01:04:10.950 --> 01:04:14.410
you will stop me, at all costs.
你要阻止我 不惜一切代价


705
01:04:15.130 --> 01:04:17.880
- You don't mean... - Just promise me, please.
- 你不是说... - 答应我, 求你了


706
01:04:21.990 --> 01:04:23.580
That's my mother.
那是我妈妈


707
01:04:27.720 --> 01:04:29.430
Sienna, wait, you can't go back!
沙织小姐 等等 你不能回去


708
01:04:29.520 --> 01:04:32.730
- You're the one she's after. - I have to help my father.
- 你才是她的目标 - 我得帮我父亲


709
01:04:34.240 --> 01:04:35.240
Okay.
好的


710
01:04:36.110 --> 01:04:37.110
I'm with you.
我支持你


711
01:04:38.030 --> 01:04:39.030
For now.
暂时


712
01:05:12.730 --> 01:05:13.730
Shut it! Shut it!
关上！关上！


713
01:05:16.360 --> 01:05:17.360
Hold.
守好


714
01:05:29.660 --> 01:05:30.620
Don't let them through!
别让他们过去


715
01:05:46.970 --> 01:05:47.930
No! No...!
不


716
01:06:01.310 --> 01:06:02.310
It's clear.
安全了


717
01:06:26.560 --> 01:06:27.670
Where's Seiya?
星矢呢？


718
01:06:28.370 --> 01:06:29.760
And whatever her name is?
还有那个谁来着？


719
01:06:29.790 --> 01:06:33.400
Sienna is not here, but I am willing to make a deal.
沙织不在, 但我愿意做个交易


720
01:06:33.470 --> 01:06:36.020
Old man, you are in no position to be making deals.
老头, 你没有资格做交易


721
01:06:36.100 --> 01:06:37.980
Wait outside, Cassios.
在外面等着, 卡西欧士


722
01:06:39.270 --> 01:06:40.730
- Are you serious? - Out!
- 你是认真的吗？ - 出去


723
01:06:48.360 --> 01:06:49.360
Hey!
嘿！


724
01:06:54.580 --> 01:06:56.620
I really need to get to this ship.
我真的需要去这艘船


725
01:07:12.180 --> 01:07:13.680
Glad you understand.
很高兴你们能理解


726
01:07:23.650 --> 01:07:25.730
How do you like my special bullets?
喜欢我的特制子弹吗？


727
01:07:31.320 --> 01:07:32.990
Let's make this easy, shall we?
让我们别搞得太复杂, 好吗？


728
01:07:33.250 --> 01:07:35.050
Just tell me where she is.
直接告诉我她在哪儿吧


729
01:07:37.250 --> 01:07:38.660
Straight to business, then.
直奔主题 呃


730
01:07:39.010 --> 01:07:40.990
What do you expect, after she almost killed me?
她差点杀了我, 你还能指望什么？


731
01:07:41.010 --> 01:07:43.220
That was an accident and you know it.
那是个意外, 你知道的


732
01:07:43.350 --> 01:07:44.810
You can't blame Sienna for it.
这不能怪沙织


733
01:07:44.890 --> 01:07:46.810
Oh, I never blamed Sienna.
我从没责怪过沙织


734
01:07:46.840 --> 01:07:48.260
I blamed you, Alman,
我怪你, 光政


735
01:07:48.710 --> 01:07:50.790
for leaving me to make all the hard choices.
怪你让我来做所有艰难的选择


736
01:07:51.160 --> 01:07:53.970
How is murdering a little girl even a choice?
谋杀一个小女孩算什么选择？


737
01:07:54.200 --> 01:07:57.160
She's a sword of Damocles hanging over all of us.
她是一把悬在我们所有人头上的达摩克利斯之剑


738
01:07:57.180 --> 01:07:59.850
- She's your daughter. - We never had a daughter!
- 她是你女儿 - 我们没有女儿


739
01:08:01.400 --> 01:08:04.240
What we had was an agreement, remember?
我们商量好了的, 记得吗？


740
01:08:04.330 --> 01:08:07.920
That when she'd go out of control, we'd do whatever had to be done together.
当她失去控制时，我们会一起做任何必须做的事情


741
01:08:08.040 --> 01:08:11.210
Sienna was entrusted to me.
沙织被托付给我


742
01:08:13.780 --> 01:08:15.330
I'm responsible for her.
我要对她负责


743
01:08:15.860 --> 01:08:17.150
I believe in her.
我相信她


744
01:08:17.330 --> 01:08:19.620
You must believe in our child too.
你也应该信任我们的孩子


745
01:08:25.330 --> 01:08:28.630
What about all the children you took to make these?
那些被你带走去做这个的孩子们怎么办？


746
01:08:31.590 --> 01:08:33.340
Weren't you responsible for them?
你不用对他们负责吗？


747
01:08:33.970 --> 01:08:35.930
It was the only way to save you.
这是拯救你的唯一办法


748
01:08:36.180 --> 01:08:38.390
And now I must save the rest of us from her.
现在, 我必须从她手中拯救我们其他人


749
01:08:48.730 --> 01:08:50.150
Speaking of the devil.
说曹操 曹操到


750
01:08:57.580 --> 01:08:58.800
Dad?
爸？


751
01:09:10.170 --> 01:09:12.970
I didn't want to do this, but I won't let you hurt her.
我也不想这么做, 但我不会让你伤害她


752
01:09:13.270 --> 01:09:14.280
I know.
我知道


753
01:09:14.470 --> 01:09:15.550
Cassios!
卡西欧士


754
01:09:24.850 --> 01:09:25.850
Enough!
够了


755
01:09:28.020 --> 01:09:30.650
Get me the girl. You can do what you want with the boy.
把女孩带给我 你想怎么处置那男孩都行


756
01:09:46.830 --> 01:09:48.210
Seiya!
星矢


757
01:09:53.550 --> 01:09:54.590
We need to go.
我们得走了


758
01:09:57.090 --> 01:10:00.010
Hey there. I'm gonna take the girl now.
你们好 我要带走那个女孩


759
01:10:00.930 --> 01:10:02.390
But first, I want you.
但首先, 我要杀了你


760
01:10:02.710 --> 01:10:03.730
Let's end this now.
让我们现在做个了结吧


761
01:10:03.800 --> 01:10:05.210
- No, Seiya. Don't. - It's okay.
- 不 星矢 别 - 没事的


762
01:10:06.560 --> 01:10:07.690
I've got the armor.
我有圣衣


763
01:10:12.650 --> 01:10:13.900
Any time now.
快点啊


764
01:10:16.700 --> 01:10:18.490
Sienna, stay back!
沙织小姐 退后


765
01:10:44.140 --> 01:10:45.930
Things have changed, kid.
今非昔比了, 小子


766
01:10:46.020 --> 01:10:48.530
Face it, you don't have what it takes.
面对现实吧, 你不具备这样的能力


767
01:11:57.380 --> 01:11:59.380
I loved these glasses.
我喜欢这副眼镜


768
01:12:44.090 --> 01:12:45.470
Stop! Stop!
住手！住手


769
01:12:46.600 --> 01:12:49.140
You've won. I'm coming with you. Let him go.
你赢了 我跟你走 放了他


770
01:12:51.230 --> 01:12:53.190
You're coming with me anyway.
反正你也要跟我走


771
01:13:13.080 --> 01:13:14.750
Rescue on the way, kids.
救援马上就到, 孩子们


772
01:13:34.770 --> 01:13:35.770
I'm sorry,
对不起


773
01:13:35.850 --> 01:13:38.730
but I'm taking you down with me.
但我要带你一起下去


774
01:13:43.200 --> 01:13:44.570
Go! Go! Go!
快走


775
01:14:40.120 --> 01:14:41.210
No.
不


776
01:15:12.590 --> 01:15:13.590
It's ready.
准备好了


777
01:15:16.830 --> 01:15:17.960
Give me a minute.
给我一分钟


778
01:15:22.130 --> 01:15:23.130
Leave.
走开


779
01:15:47.990 --> 01:15:50.860
You must think I'm the worst mother in the world.
你一定认为我是世界上最糟糕的母亲


780
01:15:51.530 --> 01:15:54.330
You... You killed Father.
你...你杀了父亲


781
01:15:55.500 --> 01:15:57.090
Alman chose his own way,
光政选择了自己了断


782
01:15:57.160 --> 01:16:00.370
and left me to clean up his mess, as always.
然后让我来收拾他的烂摊子 一如既往


783
01:16:09.590 --> 01:16:11.390
Athena's Cosmo is too strong.
雅典娜的小宇宙太强大了


784
01:16:12.170 --> 01:16:13.960
It won't fix you.
救不了你的


785
01:16:14.050 --> 01:16:14.890
I know.
我知道


786
01:16:17.050 --> 01:16:20.720
Yeah. I gave up on fixing this body a long time ago.
是啊, 我早就放弃修复这具躯体了


787
01:16:26.780 --> 01:16:29.280
We both have a bomb ticking inside.
我们的体内都有一颗炸弹在滴答作响


788
01:16:30.700 --> 01:16:35.830
Except yours is gonna be so much louder if we let it go off.
只不过如果任由它爆炸, 你的那个声音会更大


789
01:16:44.380 --> 01:16:46.340
I know I'm doing the right thing.
我知道我做得对


790
01:16:52.340 --> 01:16:55.640
I just wanted you to know it doesn't make it any easier.
我只是想让你知道, 这并不会让你变得好受一点点


791
01:17:09.650 --> 01:17:10.900
Will it hurt much?
会很疼吗？


792
01:17:13.700 --> 01:17:14.700
I don't know.
我不知道


793
01:17:37.640 --> 01:17:39.010
We need to start.
我们要开始了


794
01:17:46.060 --> 01:17:47.190
Do it.
动手吧


795
01:18:02.070 --> 01:18:04.140
能量消耗

796
01:18:34.020 --> 01:18:35.070
Sienna...
沙织小姐...


797
01:18:46.420 --> 01:18:48.210
That ain't gonna help, kiddo.
那没用的, 孩子


798
01:18:50.320 --> 01:18:51.940
I let her get taken.
我看着她被抓走了


799
01:18:52.920 --> 01:18:53.920
I failed.
我失败了


800
01:18:56.800 --> 01:18:57.880
We all did.
我们都是


801
01:18:58.470 --> 01:19:00.100
I was supposed to protect her.
我本该保护她


802
01:19:00.240 --> 01:19:03.080
Things don't always work out the way we expect them to.
事情并不总是如我们所愿


803
01:19:13.690 --> 01:19:14.990
Come on, Seiya.
来吧, 星矢


804
01:19:37.820 --> 01:19:39.080
Marin.
魔铃


805
01:19:42.100 --> 01:19:43.510
You were right about me.
你对我的看法是对的


806
01:19:45.470 --> 01:19:46.480
I failed.
我失败了


807
01:19:50.150 --> 01:19:51.310
I'm not a knight.
我不是圣斗士


808
01:19:53.320 --> 01:19:54.650
I couldn't save her.
我救不了她


809
01:19:55.930 --> 01:20:00.770
A knight should not mistake obsession for purpose.
圣斗士不应将痴迷误当成使命


810
01:20:06.830 --> 01:20:09.160
Seiya, focus.
星矢, 集中注意力


811
01:20:09.810 --> 01:20:12.160
Who is it that you're trying to save?
你拼命想要救的是谁？


812
01:20:19.590 --> 01:20:20.430
Pat.
星华


813
01:20:26.310 --> 01:20:27.390
What does this...?
这是什么....？


814
01:20:28.080 --> 01:20:30.500
<i>Who are you really trying to save?</i>
<i>你真正想救的到底是谁？</i>


815
01:20:55.290 --> 01:20:56.420
I'm sorry.
对不起


816
01:20:57.420 --> 01:20:59.170
I'm so sorry.
我很抱歉


817
01:21:13.570 --> 01:21:14.610
I know.
我知道


818
01:21:16.860 --> 01:21:17.900
It's okay.
没关系


819
01:21:20.870 --> 01:21:22.160
It wasn't your fault.
这不是你的错


820
01:21:23.910 --> 01:21:24.910
Okay.
好的


821
01:21:44.590 --> 01:21:45.720
I'll bring her back.
我会带她回来的


822
01:21:54.730 --> 01:21:55.850
I promise.
我保证


823
01:21:56.560 --> 01:21:57.610
Okay.
好的


824
01:22:07.740 --> 01:22:09.450
Let's go get Sienna back.
我们去把沙织小姐救回来


825
01:22:28.530 --> 01:22:29.870
How long will it take?
需要多长时间？


826
01:22:30.390 --> 01:22:33.600
To kill a god? Good question.
杀死一个神？问得好


827
01:22:33.680 --> 01:22:35.100
We're about to find out.
我们马上就知道了


828
01:23:03.540 --> 01:23:06.710
Oh, boy. They got us on radar.
天啊 我们被雷达发现了


829
01:23:06.800 --> 01:23:08.220
- What? - Get ready.
- 什么？ - 准备好


830
01:23:08.300 --> 01:23:09.300
For what?
准备什么？


831
01:23:09.890 --> 01:23:13.060
I can get you close, but I can't land.
我可以让你靠近点, 但我没办法着陆


832
01:23:14.390 --> 01:23:15.430
Parachute?
降落伞？


833
01:23:17.940 --> 01:23:19.810
Who says you're not funny?
谁说你不搞笑的？


834
01:23:21.900 --> 01:23:23.570
It's now or never!
机不可失, 时不再来！


835
01:23:26.230 --> 01:23:27.350
Open the doors.
开门


836
01:23:38.420 --> 01:23:40.040
Get yourself out of here!
快离开这里


837
01:23:41.340 --> 01:23:42.630
Godspeed, kiddo.
祝你好运, 孩子


838
01:25:17.510 --> 01:25:19.020
- Out of the way. - Hey!
- 别挡路 - 嘿


839
01:25:20.140 --> 01:25:21.390
He's mine.
他是我的


840
01:25:23.780 --> 01:25:26.080
Big deal. You know how to glow.
好大牌 你是懂抢镜的


841
01:25:26.200 --> 01:25:29.000
Step aside, Cassios, if you don't wanna get hurt.
靠边站 卡西欧士 如果你不想受伤的话


842
01:25:29.030 --> 01:25:29.860
Hurt?
受伤？


843
01:25:31.530 --> 01:25:34.030
You should've died when you had the chance.
你有机会的时候真应该死了算了


844
01:25:51.550 --> 01:25:53.130
What was it that you said, Cassios?
你说过什么来着, 卡西欧士？


845
01:25:55.260 --> 01:25:56.260
Right.
对了


846
01:26:00.350 --> 01:26:01.180
Oh, no.
哦, 不


847
01:26:01.810 --> 01:26:03.060
Things have changed.
今非昔比了


848
01:26:10.610 --> 01:26:13.780
Finally, the goddess Athena reveals herself.
终于, 雅典娜女神现身了


849
01:26:19.950 --> 01:26:22.200
<i>You must believe in our child too.</i>
<i>你也该信任我们的孩子</i>


850
01:26:27.790 --> 01:26:30.300
Stop! Stop the procedure!
停止！停止程序！


851
01:26:30.580 --> 01:26:32.400
It'll be over soon.
很快就结束了


852
01:26:32.420 --> 01:26:33.670
Now!
现在


853
01:26:34.510 --> 01:26:36.430
We are not stopping!
我们不会停的！


854
01:26:36.800 --> 01:26:38.390
Get out of my way.
让开


855
01:26:39.890 --> 01:26:40.970
Guards!
警卫


856
01:26:44.980 --> 01:26:47.350
Your services are no longer required.
不需要你的服务了


857
01:26:47.440 --> 01:26:49.060
There's no stopping it now.
现在已经停不下来了


858
01:26:49.170 --> 01:26:52.170
In moments, she'll be nothing but a memory.
顷刻间, 她将只剩下回忆


859
01:26:55.150 --> 01:26:56.240
Kill him!
杀了他


860
01:27:59.970 --> 01:28:01.890
You said it yourself, Guraad.
你自己说的, 古拉杜


861
01:28:02.600 --> 01:28:06.980
When one goes to war with the gods, sacrifices must be made.
当一个人与众神开战时, 必须做出牺牲


862
01:28:08.890 --> 01:28:11.770
There must be another way to protect humanity.
一定还有其他方法可以保护人类


863
01:28:12.040 --> 01:28:13.790
Protect humanity?
保护人类？


864
01:28:14.190 --> 01:28:15.950
Is that what you think you're doing?
这就是你以为你在做的事情？


865
01:28:35.170 --> 01:28:37.390
Killing Athena was only half of the battle.
杀死雅典娜 战斗才进行了一半


866
01:28:45.860 --> 01:28:48.140
This is the other half.
这是另一半


867
01:28:50.520 --> 01:28:51.900
The gold armor.
黄金圣衣


868
01:29:05.410 --> 01:29:06.950
Can't let you do that.
不能让你这么做


869
01:29:07.040 --> 01:29:09.120
Thought you were the only knight in town?
你以为你是这里唯一的圣斗士吗？


870
01:29:09.750 --> 01:29:11.120
You gotta get out of the way.
你最好把路让开


871
01:30:24.660 --> 01:30:25.490
Sienna!
沙织


872
01:30:57.190 --> 01:30:59.270
You're no match for the Phoenix.
你不是凤凰座的对手


873
01:31:10.580 --> 01:31:12.340
Why do you try so hard?
你为什么这么拼命？


874
01:31:13.850 --> 01:31:15.230
She's not worth it.
她不值得


875
01:31:15.850 --> 01:31:17.690
She's not even human.
她甚至不是人类


876
01:31:18.630 --> 01:31:20.660
Sienna's not a god of war.
沙织不是战争之神


877
01:31:20.770 --> 01:31:23.210
I don't care what kind of god she is.
我不管她是什么样的神


878
01:31:23.300 --> 01:31:24.840
Man needs no gods!
人类不需要神明！


879
01:31:59.500 --> 01:32:01.290
You don't know when to quit.
你不知道什么时候该放弃


880
01:32:01.380 --> 01:32:02.840
People keep telling me that.
人们老是这么说我


881
01:32:44.800 --> 01:32:46.800
Stop, you fool!
住手, 你这个傻瓜！


882
01:33:22.540 --> 01:33:24.000
Sienna!
沙织小姐


883
01:33:24.630 --> 01:33:27.050
Listen to me! That's not your friend anymore!
听我说 那不再是你的朋友了


884
01:33:30.630 --> 01:33:32.550
She's become the goddess of war.
她成了战争女神


885
01:33:32.630 --> 01:33:34.010
We have to stop her!
我们必须阻止她！


886
01:34:29.570 --> 01:34:30.780
<i>Seiya.</i>
<i>星矢</i>


887
01:34:30.860 --> 01:34:32.190
<i>I'm losing control.</i>
<i>我失控了</i>


888
01:34:33.950 --> 01:34:36.820
<i>I don't think I can hold her back much longer.</i>
<i>我想我再也不能拖住她了</i>


889
01:34:43.540 --> 01:34:45.580
<i>You can't save me,</i>
<i>你救不了我</i>


890
01:34:45.670 --> 01:34:48.090
<i>but you can stop Athena.</i>
<i>但你可以阻止雅典娜</i>


891
01:34:50.000 --> 01:34:51.510
<i>You must do it now.</i>
<i>你必须现在就动手</i>


892
01:34:52.340 --> 01:34:53.760
<i>At all costs.</i>
<i>不惜一切代价</i>


893
01:35:49.310 --> 01:35:50.440
Sienna...
沙织小姐...


894
01:35:52.070 --> 01:35:53.400
you're not a goddess of war.
你不是战争女神


895
01:35:55.290 --> 01:35:56.960
No one's destiny...
没有人的命运...


896
01:35:57.860 --> 01:35:59.360
is written in stone.
是一成不变的


897
01:36:02.270 --> 01:36:03.600
Not even yours.
你的也不行


898
01:36:10.910 --> 01:36:12.700
The guardian of mankind...
人类的守护神


899
01:36:13.500 --> 01:36:15.170
or a petulant jerk...
或是一个傲娇鬼...


900
01:36:17.920 --> 01:36:21.430
whatever you choose to be, I'll never give up on you.
无论你选择做哪一个, 我都不会放弃你


901
01:37:22.820 --> 01:37:23.820
Seiya.
星矢


902
01:37:33.580 --> 01:37:34.830
What? Why?
啥？为什么？


903
01:37:35.420 --> 01:37:38.090
- What was that for? - Who's the petulant jerk?
- 这是干什么？ - 谁是傲娇鬼？


904
01:37:38.760 --> 01:37:39.800
Oh, my...
哦, 我的...


905
01:37:40.820 --> 01:37:41.990
Okay.
好的


906
01:37:43.790 --> 01:37:45.350
- Get up. - Okay.
- 起来 - 好的


907
01:37:51.850 --> 01:37:53.350
Let's get out of here.
我们走吧


908
01:37:55.520 --> 01:37:56.520
Wait.
等等


909
01:38:26.140 --> 01:38:27.360
I'm sorry.
对不起


910
01:38:28.390 --> 01:38:29.890
I was wrong about you.
我看错你了


911
01:38:31.310 --> 01:38:34.520
I wasn't so sure myself for a very long time.
很长时间里, 我自己也不太确定


912
01:39:20.270 --> 01:39:21.900
You didn't have to do that.
你没必要这么做


913
01:39:24.190 --> 01:39:25.240
Yes, I did.
有必要


914
01:39:44.800 --> 01:39:46.130
Did I do this?
这是我干的吗？


915
01:39:52.640 --> 01:39:53.640
Mylock!
晨己


916
01:39:54.180 --> 01:39:55.310
Sienna!
沙织小姐


917
01:39:58.940 --> 01:39:59.940
Are you okay?
你还好吗？


918
01:40:00.440 --> 01:40:01.440
I'm okay.
我没事


919
01:40:11.660 --> 01:40:12.990
Glad you made it, Seiya.
很高兴你做到了, 星矢


920
01:40:14.290 --> 01:40:15.290
You too.
你也一样


921
01:41:01.210 --> 01:41:02.630
So, boss...
那么, 老板...


922
01:41:04.540 --> 01:41:05.880
what do we do now?
我们现在该怎么办？


923
01:41:07.840 --> 01:41:11.830
Athena's awakening is a sign the old gods will soon return and try to start a war.
雅典娜的觉醒预示着旧神即将回归, 并试图发动战争


924
01:41:14.350 --> 01:41:17.140
We need to gather all the Knights of the Zodiac to stop them.
我们需要召集所有黄道十二宫的圣斗士来阻止他们


925
01:41:21.310 --> 01:41:24.310
I'm at your service, my lord.
愿为您效劳, 我的主人


926
01:41:28.100 --> 01:41:29.930
Stop. Don't call me that.
少来 别这么叫我


927
01:41:30.030 --> 01:41:31.450
Whatever you say, princess.
随你怎么说 公主


928
01:41:32.700 --> 01:41:34.570
No. And definitely not that.
不, 千万别叫我这个


929
01:41:42.680 --> 01:41:45.620
Before we gather the knights, there's something else we need to do.
在召集圣斗士之前 我们还有一件事要做


930
01:41:46.210 --> 01:41:47.420
What's that?
那是什么？


931
01:41:50.130 --> 01:41:52.050
It's time to find Patricia.
是时候去找到星华了


932
01:41:57.220 --> 01:41:58.220
Thank you.
谢谢


933
01:41:59.730 --> 01:42:01.390
It's the least a goddess could do.
这是女神最起码应该做的


934
01:44:02.100 --> 01:44:08.490
《圣斗士星矢》
